秒"},{"pid":"1b13a20ad34c771aa326c5f1d86d74fd16bd2d4f","tid":2340398,"uid":16284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af960979ac82a1ba340e3cb50a3459fe371e883d","tid":2340398,"uid":250905,"like":25,"dislike":2,"score":23,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T12:08:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2f2znLz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2f2znLz.jpg&h=9f97da26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CZnSTSf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCZnSTSf.jpg&h=9628c12b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r6tuV5z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr6tuV5z.jpg&h=bc264b32&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T14:17:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16f5b3f1772223c733d3f4c9e39a1ff6cd3e2e7d","tid":2340398,"uid":159083,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T14:19:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.kwuntung.net/check/focus/focusdetail.php?focus_ID=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.kwuntung.net%2Fcheck%2Ffocus%2Ffocusdetail.php%3Ffocus_ID%3D2&d=E3iW9F3hP8nhDbvOoRyiQB5CyLKXDv55u35dva0wydI%3D&h=65377a4a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.kwuntung.net/check/focus/focusdetail.php?focus_ID=2</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n捶、搥、錘、鎚、椎、槌<br />\n<br />\n「錘」和「鎚」互通，兩者使用率相若。「錘/鎚」既可作動詞用，也可作名詞用。「槌」則只可作名詞用。「槌」和「錘/鎚」都解敲打用的工具，但槌子通常是木造的，錘子則必有金屬。所以「鼓槌」不會寫成「鼓錘」。<br />\n<br />\n「捶」和「搥」互通，兩者使用率相若。「捶/搥」只可作動詞用，不可作名詞用。「錘/鎚」既可作動詞用，也可作名詞用。兩者作動詞用都解擊打，但「捶/搥」是指用槌子或用拳頭擊打，「錘/鎚」則是指用金屬的鎚子擊打。所以「捶胸頓足」用「捶」（用拳頭擊打），「千錘百煉」用「錘」（用金屬的錘子擊打）。"}]}